snippet.title: Unidentify Giant sea creature attack Caught on camera, attack birds during japan tsunami.NEW

localized.description: Giant creature from the Sea attack birds (caught on camera) during Japan tsunami. I discover this unknown creature attacking birds, and showing no fear even the disaster could not stop this monster. i notice this while watching Japan tsunami video on youtube dated (Sept 2013), and decided to publish this early 2014 . see the size it is more than human size and compare to the boat anchored beside the river. find it on youtube  to prove that this is not edited.
